'''Captain Khalidi''' is the captain of station 88 of the [[Seattle Fire Department]].

==History==
Captain Khalidi led his team to a scene where a building was on fire. They started fighting the fire, but didn't have sufficient resources to do search and rescue, so when station 19 arrived, he sent them to do that. Once the first had been put out and they had evacuated a security guard and twelve women being held in a secret room, Khalidi thanked them for their help.

==Career==
He is the captain of [[Seattle Fire Department]] Station 88.
